Federal Realty Investment Trust said itsmanagement has been authorized to purchase up to one mln of itscommon shares at current market prices in open markettransactions.    The company had 13.6 mln shares outstanding as of September30.    The company said it was making the purchases because itsstock represented an excellent investment in light of currentmarket conditions.    Federal Realty will finance the buy-back through availablecash funds. Reuter&#3;